casebody.data:
No. 11-7342 (11A484). Reginald Brooks, Petitioner v. Ohio. 565 U.S. 1047, 132 S. Ct. 607,

181 L. Ed. 2d 446,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 8289. November 15, 2011.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death, presented to Justice Kagan, and by her referred to the Court, denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Ohio, Cuyahoga County, denied.
